ThinkPart(
    type='think',
    think="The task is essentially complete. Let me summarize what was done:\n\n
1. **Identified the bug**: The `Makefile` build target built `apps/api` before `
packages/shared-types`, causing `nest build` to fail with `TS2307: Cannot find m
odule '@social-world/shared-types'` because the shared-types package hadn't been
compiled yet. This was exposed by PR #58's `f68dbfd` commit which added imports 
from `@social-world/shared-types` in `im.gateway.ts`.\n\n2. **Fixed the Makefile
**: Reordered the build steps so `packages/shared-types` is built before `apps/a
pi`.\n\n3. **Fixed E2E install error handling**: Updated `.maestro/scripts/run-e
2e.sh` to properly fail when APK installation fails, instead of silently continu
ing due to `grep | true`.\n\n4. **Added regression test**: Created `tests/struct
ure/test_makefile_build_order.py` to validate that `packages/shared-types` is bu
ilt before `apps/api`.\n\n5. **Verified all tests pass**: \n   - `make build` ✅
\n   - `make test` ✅\n   - `make test-bdd` ✅\n   - `make lint` ✅\n   - `make 
test-mobile-e2e-login` ✅ (after fixing environment: seeding Redis SMS code and 
freeing port 7001)\n\n6. **Committed and pushed**: \n   - Commit: `fix: resolve 
#58 - E2E for Issue #58`\n   - Pushed to `feat/issue-5`\n   - PR #58 already exi
sts and now includes this fix\n\nThe task is complete.",
    encrypted=None
)
TextPart(
    type='text',
    text='## 任务完成 ✅\n\n### 修复内容\n\n**Issue #58: E2E for Issue #58**\n\n
本次修复解决了 PR #58（IM 即时通讯功能）引入的两个关键问题：\n\n#### 1. Makefile
构建顺序错误（`Makefile`）\n**根因**：`f68dbfd` 在 `apps/api/src/modules/im/im.g
ateway.ts` 中引入了对 `@social-world/shared-types` 的导入，但 `Makefile` 的 `bui
ld` 目标先构建 `apps/api` 再构建 `packages/shared-types`。由于 `nest build`（tsc
）需要 `packages/shared-types/dist/index.js` 存在，导致 `make build` 和 `make te
st-bdd` 失败：\n```\nTS2307: Cannot find module \'@social-world/shared-types\'\n
```\n\n**修复**：将 `cd packages/shared-types && npm run build` 移至 `apps/api` 
之前。\n\n#### 2. E2E APK 安装错误被静默忽略（`.maestro/scripts/run-e2e.sh`）\n*
*根因**：原脚本使用 `$ADB install ... | grep -E "Success|Failed|adb:" || true`，
导致无论安装成功还是失败，`grep` 匹配后整体管道返回 0，脚本继续执行。这意味着 AP
K 安装失败时 E2E 仍会继续运行，造成难以排查的错误。\n\n**修复**：改为显式检查 `a
db install` 输出是否包含 `"Success"`，若不包含则打印错误并 `exit 1`。\n\n#### 3.
回归测试（`tests/structure/test_makefile_build_order.py`）\n新增结构测试，确保 `
packages/shared-types` 始终在 `apps/api` 之前构建，防止后续变更破坏构建顺序。\n\
n### 验证结果\n\n| 检查项 | 结果 |\n|--------|------|\n| `make build` | ✅ 通过 
